name: Casey James Logo
description:
This is a fully designed logo and will only be sold one time.

HOW TO ORDER
During the checkout process, please include the following within the Special Instructions:

YOUR COMPANY NAME
YOUR COLORS (please be as specific as possible)
ANY SPECIAL INSTRUCTIONS

Please allow 1 – 2 business days for us to prepare your logo. After we have prepared your logo, we will email you a proof(s) of the image for you to review. Once approved, we will send you:

•A PNG FILE (Hi-Res)
•A JPG FILE (Hi-Res)
•Additional files available upon request

Forgot to include your Company Name and Colors during checkout? No problem. Simply email us at orders@bellablucreations.com.
